This project is for building a custom LLM server/wrapper that will be deployed to a cloud server. This is used to intercept the request from Agora ConvoAI, do our own processing, then send it back to Agora. 

Currently Agora ConvoAI follow this process

User speaks (RTC) ---> Agora Server (process ASR audio-to-text) ---> LLM server (receive text input, then output text) ---> Agora Server (process the text, convert text to speech) ---> User hears the AI output

In the new process, I want to intercept the request like so 

User speaks (RTC) ---> Agora Server (process ASR audio-to-text) ---> Custom LLM wrapper (do my own process, adding tools, RAG, etc) --> LLM server (receive text input, then output text) ---> Custom LLM wrapper ---> Agora Server (process the text, convert text to speech) ---> User hears the AI output

For the custom LLM wrapper, i can add additional logic such as RAG, tools, etc. before sending it to the official LLM for processing. In this project, I want to add some async DIFY tasks/workflows. 

