## Option 4: Google Cloud Run (serverless containers)

```bash
# Build and push to Artifact Registry
gcloud auth configure-docker us-central1-docker.pkg.dev
gcloud artifacts repositories create agora-custom-llm \
    --repository-format=docker --location=us-central1

IMAGE=us-central1-docker.pkg.dev/$PROJECT_ID/agora-custom-llm/app:latest
docker build -t $IMAGE .
docker push $IMAGE

# Deploy
gcloud run deploy agora-custom-llm \
    --image $IMAGE \
    --region us-central1 \
    --platform managed \
    --allow-unauthenticated \
    --port 8000 \
    --memory 512Mi \
    --set-env-vars "OPENAI_BASE_URL=https://api.openai.com/v1,OPENAI_MODEL=gpt-4o-mini,LOG_LEVEL=INFO,TOOLS_CONFIG=config/tools.yaml" \
    --set-secrets "OPENAI_API_KEY=openai-api-key:latest"
```

**Note:** Cloud Run scales to zero when idle (cold starts). For always-on, set `--min-instances 1`.

