## Agora ConvoAI wiring (all providers)

Once deployed, set the custom LLM URL in your ConvoAI join config:

```json
{
  "llm": {
    "vendor": "custom",
    "url": "https://<your-deployed-host>/chat/completions",
    "api_key": "any-non-empty-string"
  }
}
```

## SSE streaming note

All reverse proxies (Nginx, ALB, Cloud Run, etc.) must be configured to **disable response buffering** for the SSE stream to reach the client in real time:

- **Nginx:** `proxy_buffering off;` (already in the example above)
- **ALB:** uses HTTP/1.1 keep-alive — no extra config needed, but set idle timeout ≥ 60s
- **Cloud Run:** streaming is enabled by default
- **Fly.io / Railway / Render:** streaming is enabled by default